# React Native App Environment Variables

# ==================== API Configuration ====================
# Required: Next.js Backend API URL
# For production:
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=https://your-nextjs-domain.com/api
# For local development:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api

# ==================== Chatbot Configuration ====================
# Optional: OpenRouter API Keys for AI chatbot functionality
# The chatbot uses a 3-key fallback system for reliability
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPEN_ROUTER_API_KEY1=your_openrouter_api_key_1
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPEN_ROUTER_API_KEY2=your_openrouter_api_key_2
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPEN_ROUTER_API_KEY3=your_openrouter_api_key_3

# ==================== Notes ====================
# - The app requires EXPO_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL to function
# - Chatbot API keys are optional but recommended for full functionality
# - Without chatbot keys, the chatbot will use rule-based responses only
# - All environment variables must start with EXPO_PUBLIC_ to be accessible in React Native
